  -> clearLoginCache()
  -> window.jobReviewAggregator.clearLoginCache()
```

主进程：

```txt
ipcMain.handle("clear-login-cache")
  -> session.defaultSession.clearStorageData({
       storages: [
         "cookies",
         "localstorage",
         "indexdb",
         "cachestorage",
         "serviceworkers"
       ]
     })
  -> session.defaultSession.clearCache()
  -> return { ok: true }
