### 8.3 清除数据库

前端：

```txt
handleClearDatabase()
  -> clearDatabase(databaseConfirmText)
  -> window.jobReviewAggregator.clearDatabase(confirmText)
```

主进程：

```txt
ipcMain.handle("clear-database", async (_event, confirmText) => {
  if (confirmText !== "清除数据库") throw Error
  const repository = activeRepository ?? createDevelopmentRepository()
  if (!repository?.clearAll) throw Error
  await repository.clearAll()
  return { ok: true }
})
```

`activeRepository`：

- 打包版内置后端启动时由 `startIntegratedServer()` 设置。
- 开发模式因为后端是独立 `npm run api` 启动的，Electron 里没有 activeRepository，所以会走 `createDevelopmentRepository()`，打开 `data/app.sqlite`。

`SQLiteReviewRepository.clearAll()`：

```txt
DELETE FROM analyses;
DELETE FROM reviews;
DELETE FROM companies;
DELETE FROM searches;
```


